<br>
She tried a few relaxation exercises, with no luck. She sat up, taking up a meditative posture and decided to try, once again, to make sense of these images. <br>
<br>
The eyes of the wolf, filled with judgment. <br>
<br>
Every time she closed her eyes now, she saw them. <br>
<br>
The eyes of the wolf, promising retribution. <br>
